## sort() function

返回根据比较器 `f` 排序的数组<!-- -->,该比较器应接受两个值。

**Signature:**

```typescript
declare function sort(
  f: (a: any, b: any) => unknown,
  iterable: readonly [],
): any[];
```

## Example

```ts
sort((a, b) => a > b, [3, 4, 1, 2, 5, 2]); // [1, 2, 2, 3, 4, 5]
sort((a, b) => a.localeCompare(b), "bcdaef"); // ["a", "b", "c", "d", "e", "f"]
```
